<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:09:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于担心以色列与真主党之间的重大战争迫在眉睫，主要航空公司取消并推迟飞往贝鲁特的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</link><description>汉莎航空、法国航空、土耳其航空、爱琴海航空和其他主要航空公司已决定推迟和取消飞往黎巴嫩唯一国际机场的航班，因为黎巴嫩、以色列和中东地区的局势可能会升级，黎巴嫩发生的袭击造成以色列境内 12 名儿童死亡。戈兰高地</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:24:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队指挥官下令炸毁拉法水库。以色列国防军怀疑违反国际法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</link><description>装甲兵炸毁水库的行为得到了指挥官的批准，但没有得到高级军官的同意。一名士兵在社交媒体上发布了视频，称其为“纪念安息日”。军方将决定是否展开正式调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</guid></item><item><title>Majdal Shams 的杀戮场上：巨大而平静的悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</link><description>德鲁兹小镇迈季达勒沙姆斯是一个风景如画、安静的山脚下的地方，在来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡后，这座小镇陷入了彻底的震动。一位居民说：“他们是我们大家的孩子。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</guid></item><item><title>我出生在以色列。我哪儿也不去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</link><description>我不打算搬家。哈马斯不会让我搬家，贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇或伊塔马尔·本-格维尔也不会</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</guid></item><item><title>11 岁德鲁兹男孩被确认为真主党火箭袭击的第 12 名受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</link><description>对火箭袭击现场发现的证据进行的 DNA 测试证实了吉瓦拉·易卜拉欣·易卜拉欣 (Jivara Ibrahim Ibrahim) 的死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:26:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列无人机袭击黎巴嫩造成两人死亡、三人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-live/12th-victim-of-attack-identified-cabinet-authorizes-pm-to-determine-response/00000190-fc64-d7a2-a9b0-fe640b290006</link><description>真主党火箭弹袭击中失踪的 11 岁受害者尸体已找到，死亡人数增至 12 人 ■ 以色列北部地区议会警告疏散定居点的居民“保持警惕并减少集会” ■ 报告：以色列国防军袭击中造成两人死亡、三人受伤黎巴嫩南部 ■ 指示 Gallant 为北部事态发展做好准备：“真主党不会从这次事件中洗刷干净”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-live/12th-victim-of-attack-identified-cabinet-authorizes-pm-to-determine-response/00000190-fc64-d7a2-a9b0-fe640b290006</guid></item><item><title>北方全面战争？以色列对 Majdal Shams 袭击的反应将是决定性因素</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/another-escalation-or-turning-point-weighing-next-steps/00000190-fafc-d87c-ab98-fffeefbf0000</link><description>以色列专家试图评估真主党可能采取的下一步行动，北部德鲁兹社区的灾难不会得不到解决。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/another-escalation-or-turning-point-weighing-next-steps/00000190-fafc-d87c-ab98-fffeefbf0000</guid></item><item><title>戈兰高地遭受袭击后，内塔尼亚胡推迟将生病和受伤的儿童从加沙疏散到阿联酋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-delays-evacuation-of-sick-wounded-children-from-gaza-to-uae-after-golan-attack/00000190-fab3-d5ef-a5fe-fabf8c750000</link><description>以色列最初同意为数百名受伤儿童从加沙运送到阿联酋接受治疗提供便利。以色列人权医生协会称这一决定是“以色列政府对儿童生命的残酷游戏”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-delays-evacuation-of-sick-wounded-children-from-gaza-to-uae-after-golan-attack/00000190-fab3-d5ef-a5fe-fabf8c750000</guid></item><item><title>为了挽救人质谈判，以色列探索内塔尼亚胡要求阻止武装加沙人向北移动的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/to-salvage-hostage-talks-israel-explores-options-to-block-armed-gazans-from-moving-north/00000190-fa94-dfcb-a1f3-fed5d6f60000</link><description>武装分子从加沙南部向北部的流动被视为内塔尼亚胡在人质协议中面临的主要挑战。随着摩萨德负责人从罗马与调解员的会谈中归来，以色列官员看到了哈马斯在谈判中灵活性增强的迹象</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 19:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/to-salvage-hostage-talks-israel-explores-options-to-block-armed-gazans-from-moving-north/00000190-fa94-dfcb-a1f3-fed5d6f60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对国会和以色列人质施展了残酷的老伎俩</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-28/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-pulled-an-old-cruel-trick-on-congress-and-on-israels-hostages/00000190-fa3e-d43d-afd2-fe3ee7710000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡来到华盛顿，对释放人质的协议表现出乐观态度，然后——在以色列公众看到他在国会受到起立鼓掌后——决定恢复他的拒绝立场</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 18:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-28/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahu-pulled-an-old-cruel-trick-on-congress-and-on-israels-hostages/00000190-fa3e-d43d-afd2-fe3ee7710000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列准备打击真主党时，西方努力避免黎巴嫩爆发全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</link><description>外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，全面战争的威胁取决于真主党对以色列袭击黎巴嫩的反应。美国和法国正试图阻止以色列以贝鲁特或其他主要城市为目标，以报复迈季代勒沙姆斯袭击事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/as-israel-prepares-to-strike-hezbollah-west-seeks-to-avert-all-out-war-in-lebanon/00000190-fa1e-d731-a9bf-ff7ec5e70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 296 天：外交官称正在努力阻止以色列袭击贝鲁特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</link><description>数千人参加真主党在德鲁兹镇火箭弹袭击中丧生的 12 名儿童和青少年的葬礼 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特表示真主党将付出沉重代价 ■ 伊朗警告以色列不要在黎巴嫩进行任何“新冒险” ■ 据报道真主党清理了前方的关键地点以色列的预期反应 ■ 这是战争进入 296 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-296-diplomats-say-efforts-underway-to-avert-israeli-strike-on-beirut/00000190-fa5c-d10b-a3b8-ff7c53260000</guid></item><item><title>这些久经沙场的以色列和美国退伍军人如何希望结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-these-battle-hardened-israeli-and-u-s-veterans-hope-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-f9b0-d10b-a3b8-fdf01c5e0000</link><description>在一项新的合作中，来自以色列“打破沉默”组织和“美国共同防御”组织的前士兵们正在宣扬他们的信念，即退伍军人拥有理解和反对不公正现象的独特能力：“我们去过那里，知道我们在谈论什么，所以人们倾向于倾听&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 17:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-these-battle-hardened-israeli-and-u-s-veterans-hope-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-f9b0-d10b-a3b8-fdf01c5e0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列军队在加沙南部深入推进；据报道20人死亡，数千人逃离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</link><description>随着以色列撤离命令促使更多人离开加沙中部和南部，以色列坦克开进了汗尤尼斯。以色列国防军表示，一名军官和一名士兵在加沙南部的战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 15:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/israeli-forces-reportedly-advance-deeper-in-south-gaza-20-reported-killed-thousands-flee/00000190-f9d8-d5ef-a5fe-fbde87be0000</guid></item><item><title>“笨拙”但沉重：真主党在迈季代勒沙姆斯发射伊朗制造的火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</link><description>Falaq 1于20世纪90年代在伊朗研制，旨在为军队提供重型火箭炮，能够打击掩体和其他目标，在叙利亚内战期间，它被真主党和叙利亚军队使用。自一月份以来，真主党已向以色列发射了数十次火箭</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:38:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/dumb-but-heavy-the-iranian-made-rocket-hezbollah-launched-at-majdal-shams/00000190-f91e-d987-a59c-f9bf20fd0000</guid></item><item><title>如果美国不否决对以色列的制裁怎么办？法律专家称“这是世界末日”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</link><description>犹太人民政策研究所副所长舒基·弗里德曼表示，对定居者实施制裁的影响不仅限于约旦河西岸，而且已经在削弱以色列的国际合法性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-if-the-u-s-doesnt-veto-sanctions-against-israel-its-the-end-of-the-world/00000190-f95b-d667-ad9f-fddb9f940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的德鲁兹社区解释说</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</link><description>以色列德鲁兹人正在哀悼在黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击戈兰高地期间丧生的 11 名儿童。这个紧密团结的社区在以色列军事和社会中发挥着关键作用，但在这些问题上也存在分歧。谁是德鲁兹人，他们与中东各地社区的关系如何，最近的战争对他们有何影响？</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 14:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/haaretz-explains/2024-07-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-druze-community-in-israel-explained/00000188-8c42-d3c4-afec-9ed397020000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列与哈马斯的人质协议还包括外国人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</link><description>据以色列军方称，有 10 名外国人在加沙地带被扣为人质，其中 7 人还活着。 ■ 警方还在调查一名自 10 月 7 日起失踪的泰国公民的案件</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 11:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/sources-say-israel-hamas-hostage-cease-fire-deal-would-include-foreign-nationals/00000190-f8b1-d901-abd6-feb9c0ed0000</guid></item><item><title>一位面临所有困难的跨巴勒斯坦妇女</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</link><description>纪录片《她的名字叫泽哈瓦》去年在海法电影节上获得了著名奖项，但战争意味着它必须等待才能重返大银幕</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/the-story-of-a-trans-palestinian-woman-who-had-all-the-odds-stacked-against-her/00000190-f8b0-df0c-ab98-ffbb1a280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部11名儿童被杀，但内塔尼亚胡并不着急</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</link><description>一个正在“七条战线”作战并出国旅行一周（包括一次特别的周末停留）的国家的元首根本不是一个领导人。他会的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:13:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-28/ty-article/.premium/12-children-killed-in-northern-israel-but-as-far-as-netanyahus-concerned-theres-no-rush/00000190-f838-d541-adbc-f9f844a40000</guid></item></channel></rss>